listitem.para:
const btTransform & getTransform (
)
The transformation is the combination of the node’s rotation,
position, and scale properties. The default transformation is
SCNMatrix4Identity.

const btQuaternion & getOrientation (
)
The rotation, eulerAngles, and orientation properties all
affect the rotational aspect of its transform property. Any change to one
of these properties is reflected in the others.
